6. What is the difference between HashMap and Hashtable?

ğŸ” Explanation:

Feature	HashMap	Hashtable

Thread-Safe	âŒ Not Thread-safe	âœ… Thread-safe (synchronized)
Null Keys/Values	âœ… 1 null key, multiple null values	âŒ No null key or value
Performance	Faster	Slower (due to sync)


âœ… Use ConcurrentHashMap in place of Hashtable in modern apps.


